@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_uohwnv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.cos(wp.sin(v1 + 0.10)))
    v1 = 0.63
    tmp = (wp.abs(wp.cos(tmp + 0.86)) / wp.abs(wp.exp(v0 + 0.72)))
    v0 = (0.29 / (v2 - v2))
    data[tid] = v0
